name: Dreaded Imperial Starfleet (V)
Lore: 'The Empire uses short-range fighters and patrol craft to maintain a presence in every system within its scope of power.',
Text: 'Deploy on table.  While you have more systems on table than opponent, your capital starships may deploy at -2 (to a maximum of -3) to battlegrounds.  When you deploy an Imperial-Class Star Destroyer, may deploy (for free) a [Death Star II] or [A New Hope] squadron there (no replacement necessary) from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)',
